Alison Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alison_Wright 0 Alison Wright (born 12 July 1976) is an English actress. She is best known for her role as Martha Hanson on the television series The Americans, for which she was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 2017. Wright's other notable roles were in the film The Accountant (2016), as well as on the television series Sneaky Pete (2015–2018) and Feud (2017).
